-mission-giver-in-the-red-flower-field.jpg\" alt=\"The mission giver in the red flower field \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The mission giver in the red flower field<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>She\u2019ll ask you to get 3 samples of Honey from Combee in the area.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/031\/03-pokemon-unbound-searching-in-the-flower-fields.jpg\" alt=\"Searching in the Flower Fields \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Searching in the Flower Fields<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Combee can be found while walking through any color of flower in Flower Paradise.<\/p>\n<p>Every Combee found is holding a Honey, so you have a few options as to acquire it:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Catch 3 Combee and take the Honey from them<\/li>\n<li>Battle 3 Combee and use <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm046-thief\/\">Thief<\/a>, Covet or Knock Off to take the items<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>When you deliver all 3 Honeys to the lady in the flower fields, she\u2019ll give you TM62 Silver Wind as thanks.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","p